'''App Store''' can refer to many [[online distribution]] platforms: *[[Amazon Appstore]], an online application distribution system for Android devices. *[[App Store (iOS)]], the official Apple online application distribution system for iPad, iPhone, and iPod Touch. *[[Mac App Store]], the official Apple online application distribution system for Mac OS X.
